arts.ttl: Valladolid strikes late to secure a 3-2 victory at Alaves in Spanish league
arts.sum: After the break, Valladolid looked more dangerous as the second half went on and it secured all three points with goals in the 72nd and 76th minutes. Two goals in the last 20 minutes gave Real Valladolid only its second win of the Spanish league season with a 3-2 victory at Alaves on Friday.
